DSCHRG_DSTNTN_CD 44D Discharge Destination Code CHAR 2 This column documents the patient's discharge destination. 01-Home (private home/apt., board/care, assisted living, group home, transitional living); 
02-Short-term General Hospital; 
03 -Skilled Nursing Facility (SNF); 
04 -Intermediate care; 
06 -Home under care of organized home health service organization; 
50 -Hospice (home); 
51 -Hospice (institutional facility); 
61 -Swing bed; 
